Sentence: Among these BiS 2 -based superconductors, EuBiS 2 F with a T c of 0.3 K is very unique because it can become super- conducting without extrinsic chemical doping .
In contrary with the situation in Eu 3 Bi 2 - S x 4 Se x F 4 , T c is suppressed upon Sr dop- ing, and SC disappears above 0.3 K at x = 2, meanwhile the resistivity becomes semiconductor-like.

Meanwhile a possible charge-density-wave transition was observed around 280 K. Via structural design, its analogous compound Eu 3 Bi 2 S 4 F 4 , with an additional EuF layer incorporating into EuBiS 2 F, which shows superconductivity at 1.5 K was also reported .
